  <files>ThermoRawFileParser/Writer/MzPeakSpectrumWriter.cs</files>
  <behavior>
    - All in-range scans (MaxLevel + MsLevel.Contains(level) + [first,last] range) contribute point rows; out-of-range scans contribute none.
    - spectrum_index is dense 0-based output ordinal, contiguous per spectrum, incremented only for emitted spectra.
    - Points per spectrum are m/z ascending; equal-m/z points keep their relative order (stable) and none are dropped or merged (count out == count in).
